\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 It writes 7 different \cf4 \cb5 \strokec4 .service\cf3 \cb1 \strokec3  files. This tells the Linux kernel: 
\f2\i "The moment this Pi receives power, automatically start the camera, the brain, the network fallbacks, and the tunnels in the background."
