\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 It issues \cf4 \cb5 \strokec4 systemctl set-default multi-user.target\cf3 \cb1 \strokec3 . This permanently kills the heavy Raspberry Pi Desktop (GUI). The Pi now boots in pure, raw terminal mode, dedicating 100% of its CPU and RAM directly to your code and video feed.\
